# Walkthrough 01 - First Contact

In this walkthrough, we'll reverse engineer the Android game **Goods Sorting** from scratch.

We'll assume we know nothing about the application.

No source code, no documentation, no prior knowledge of the game or the technologies it uses.

Our objective is simply to answer one question.

> **How does this application work?**

